WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 22=

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:05.919
My child!

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:06.920
Let go!

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:15.759
Hey!

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:16.639
It's bugs!

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:17.720
Bugs!

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.079
Run!

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:21.160
No!

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:22.759
How could this happen?

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:23.999
My child!

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.520
Madam!

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:27.799
Madam, are you alright?

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.519
Why was it raising bugs?

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:31.600
(What a vicious scheme.)

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:48.880
Who was it?

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:54.000
Who killed my plant spirit?

00:00:55.640 --> 00:00:59.360
I want...

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.280
Alright, all the bad things
are gone now.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.360
Thank you, Little Princess.

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.160
By the way,

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.320
what was that swaddled bundle about?

00:01:33.040 --> 00:01:36.680
I clearly remember the Imperial Preceptor
giving it to me himself,

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:38.760
saying it was a sacred object
that would help me.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:40.200
The Imperial Preceptor?

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:43.560
He personally came last night.

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:46.040
He said I was originally fated
to have a son,

00:01:46.160 --> 00:01:48.000
but someone had ruined my fortune.

00:01:48.600 --> 00:01:50.400
So he specially came
to grant me an opportunity.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.440
Outrageous.

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:54.280
This is absolutely outrageous.

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:56.399
Your Highness,

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.960
I'm back.

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:01.119
Greetings, Madam Ning.
Greetings, Little Princess.

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:02.640
Uncle Shiwan, what happened?

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.000
Ah...

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:04.999
Little Princess,

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:07.039
following your
and Your Highness's orders,

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:09.839
I stayed guarding outside
the Ning Residence.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:10.639
But unexpectedly,

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:13.639
after Ning Huchen learned
his wife had gone missing,

00:02:13.640 --> 00:02:15.039
not only was he not worried,

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:15.960
he...

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:19.639
He actually

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:20.840
turned around and

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:23.399
went back home drinking

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.959
with his cousin Lady Liu in his arms.

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:25.959
He is...

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.560
Just as expected.

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:31.080
The Imperial Preceptor set the trap,
and Ning Huchen played along.

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:34.159
One wanted to harm her
and seize her fortune, and the other wanted...

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:35.920
I'm going to settle the score
with him right now!

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:37.280
Little Princess, leave it to me.

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:40.759
I've been sick all these years,

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.680
not dead all these years.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.400
Help me change.

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:52.519
I've been married to Ning Huchen
for over ten years.

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:53.239
His rice shop,

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:53.919
his fortune...

00:02:53.920 --> 00:02:56.200
which part wasn't built
with my family's money?

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.200
Since he wants to be shameless,

00:02:59.000 --> 00:02:59.839
then

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.800
I'll tear off his mask myself.

00:03:04.780 --> 00:03:07.020
(Ning Residence)

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:15.960
Master,

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:19.639
Madam fainted in the street
and her whereabouts are unknown.

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:22.560
(Steward Lin, Ning Residence)
I'm afraid things look grim.

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:25.840
Good.

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:29.160
The Imperial Preceptor
truly is remarkable.

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:30.760
Master,

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.760
now that that old hag is dead,

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:35.199
doesn't all her private property
belong to us now?

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:38.160
I've been thinking about it for ages.

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:43.040
Don't worry.

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:46.400
I've already
prepared everything for you.

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:50.280
Men.

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:55.320
Bring Madam's private treasury here.

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.840
What's going on?

00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:20.839
Why has it all turned into spirit money?

00:04:20.840 --> 00:04:22.279
The road to the underworld is long.

00:04:22.280 --> 00:04:24.120
Naturally, I had to prepare
enough travel money

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:25.720
for the two of you.

00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:42.019
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:42.020 --> 00:04:45.859
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:45.860 --> 00:04:49.379
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:52.340
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:53.220 --> 00:04:56.859
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:56.860 --> 00:05:00.620
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:00.700 --> 00:05:04.019
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:04.020 --> 00:05:08.060
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:13.660 --> 00:05:17.339
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:20.979
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:20.980 --> 00:05:24.699
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:28.339
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:28.340 --> 00:05:32.019
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:33.939
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:33.940 --> 00:05:40.140
♪Good fortune♪